    "Expand along first row:",
    "$D=2\\begin{vmatrix}-6 & 0 \\\\ -27 & -4\\end{vmatrix}-7\\begin{vmatrix}-1 & 0 \\\\ 0 & -4\\end{vmatrix}+1\\begin{vmatrix}-1 & -6 \\\\ 0 & -27\\end{vmatrix}$.",
    "$=2(24)-7(4)+1(27)=48-28+27=47$."
