  "question": "If $A=\\begin{pmatrix} \\alpha & 2 \\\\ 2 & \\alpha \\end{pmatrix}$ and $|A^3|=27$, then the value of $\\alpha$ is",
  "options": [
    "(a) ±1",
    "(b) ±2",
    "(c) ±√5",
    "(d) ±√7"
  ],
  "solutionSteps": [
